#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.17"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.17:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.17:0.2"
msgid "2. Dhammacakkappavattanavagga "
msgstr "2. Rolling Forth the Wheel of Dhamma "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Avijjāsutta "
msgstr "17. Ignorance "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn56.17:1.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Seated to one side, that mendicant said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.17:1.2"
msgid "“‘avijjā, avijjā’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘ignorance’. "

msgctxt "sn56.17:1.3"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, bhante, avijjā; "
msgstr "What is ignorance? "

msgctxt "sn56.17:1.4"
msgid "kittāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti? "
msgstr "And how is an ignorant person defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.17:1.5"
msgid "“Yaṃ kho, bhikkhu, dukkhe aññāṇaṃ, dukkhasamudaye aññāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhe aññāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya aññāṇaṃ—"
msgstr "“Not knowing about suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. "

msgctxt "sn56.17:1.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, avijjā; "
msgstr "This is called ignorance. "

msgctxt "sn56.17:1.7"
msgid "ettāvatā ca avijjāgato hotīti. "
msgstr "And this is how an ignorant person is defined. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.17:2.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhu, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.17:2.2"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
